<BaseLayout title="Terms of Use | CourtScope"><section class="hero"><div class="prose-width"><p class="eyebrow">Public policy</p><h1>Terms of Use</h1><p class="lede">Use CourtScope as civic information, not as a substitute for legal advice or official records.</p></div></section><section class="section"><div class="prose-width"><div class="card"><p>You may not use the site or datasets for harassment, doxxing, discrimination, voter suppression, unlawful profiling, automated legal decisions, judicial targeting, or unauthorized resale. Dataset-specific terms control reuse.</p><h2>What controls</h2><p>Official source terms, applicable law, dataset-specific notices, and the current published CourtScope methodology control where they are more specific. Contact <a href="mailto:info@courtscope.org">info@courtscope.org</a> for questions.</p><p><strong>Last updated:</strong> July 11, 2026</p></div></div></section></BaseLayout>